72 750 Td
(  Bytes 0-7: Cell voltages 1-4 \(16-bit each, resolution 1 mV\).) Tj
72 736 Td
(  Cycle time: 500 ms.) Tj
72 722 Td
(VX-IRS-C005: CAN message 0x1B0 - Fault Code.) Tj
72 708 Td
(  Byte 0: Fault category \(0=none, 1=voltage, 2=thermal, 3=comm, 4=hardware\).) Tj
72 694 Td
(  Byte 1-2: Fault code \(see DTC table in section 5\).) Tj
72 680 Td
(  Byte 3: Severity \(0=info, 1=warning, 2=critical\).) Tj
72 666 Td
() Tj
72 652 Td
(3. LIN Bus Interface \(Optional Diagnostic Extension\)) Tj
72 638 Td
(VX-IRS-L001: LIN version 2.1. Baud rate: 19.2 kbps.) Tj
72 624 Td
(VX-IRS-L002: BMS acts as LIN slave. Diagnostic master: vehicle gateway ECU.) Tj
72 610 Td
(VX-IRS-L003: LIN frame 0x20: read individual cell voltages \(cells 1-8 per frame\).) Tj
72 596 Td
() Tj
72 582 Td
(4. Power Supply Interface) Tj
72 568 Td
(VX-IRS-P001: Supply voltage: 12 V nominal, range 9 V to 16 V. See HAG-REQ-P002.) Tj
72 554 Td
(VX-IRS-P002: Inrush current shall not exceed 2 A for more than 10 ms at power-up.) Tj
72 540 Td
(VX-IRS-P003: Reverse polarity protection required. Clamp diode minimum 40 V / 5 A.) Tj
72 526 Td
(VX-IRS-P004: BMS KL15 wake-up input: active high, 12 V logic, hysteresis 0.5 V.) Tj
72 512 Td
() Tj
72 498 Td
(5. Mechanical Interface) Tj
72 484 Td
(VX-IRS-M001: Connector: 48-pin sealed automotive connector. Mating half specified by OEM.) Tj
72 470 Td
(VX-IRS-M002: Mounting: 4x M6 screws, torque 8 Nm plus or minus 1 Nm.) Tj
72 456 Td
(VX-IRS-M003: Enclosure dimensions: 180 mm x 120 mm x 45 mm. Weight < 850 g.) Tj
ET

